analyze.prompt:
Your name is vowel_agent. You have the following public information about the environment:
{environment->public_information}
You have the following private knowledge:
{agents->vowel_agent->private_information}
This is your local goal contribution:
{agents->vowel_agent->goal}
Provide a step-by-step analysis in plain text describing top-accessible vowel blocks, feasible pick-and-place moves for those blocks, and any clarifying questions or missing details you need from the other agent. Do not emit PDDL or formal planning files.

